{"tid":355542,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NGT討論區第12回︰歡迎乃區手足過嚟吹水,多謝支持!!!","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T11:29:20.000Z","uid":46420,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"535344e6ad2ac94ac25eeec04a82f94d6b3c76b3","tid":355542,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">溫馨提示：<br />\n「邊個回post不開post,<br />\n祝你生活很糟糕」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNGT48是日本一個由作詞家秋元康擔任製作人的女子偶像團體，主要的活動據點是日本北陸地方北端的主要城市新潟。2015年8月21日於新潟市歷史博物館正式公開，自此展開活動。NGT48的團名是以根據地新潟的羅馬音簡寫（羅馬拼音為NIIGATA），是AKB48第7個姊妹團體、以及第5個國內姊妹團體。<br />\n<img src=\"http://ngt48.jp/resources/ckeditor_assets/000/012/001/12001-ngt48_profile_up.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fngt48.jp%2Fresources%2Fckeditor_assets%2F000%2F012%2F001%2F12001-ngt48_profile_up.png%3F&h=30ec03b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/b5paOGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb5paOGf.jpg&h=92170641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1362pjmv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1362pjmv&h=6ef4f2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNGT48 1st Anniversary - <span style=\"color: red;\">好評發售中</span><br />\n1. 這po有沒有版規?<br />\n無，我地好自由。不過請尊重成員及唔好人身攻擊其他會員。另外，新人加入時如有心儀的推請講低，方便大家討論。<br />\n2. 如果討論其他48G姊妹團或46友團會否引起世界大戰？<br />\n絕對唔會，不用分哪麼細，錢都是肥秋賺。<br />\n3. NGT有咩好歌推介?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn-iXRXpfVTs&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b3e0dff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs</a><br />\n4. 除了NGT48，有沒有其他推介？<br />\nAKB 千葉惠里<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRLa2ASvp7M2Ex6TnWgeG6g_PQvxSksssXYZdNVFOBzDRo9vSki8Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRLa2ASvp7M2Ex6TnWgeG6g_PQvxSksssXYZdNVFOBzDRo9vSki8Q&h=4a2a31ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎新人加入<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舊po回帶：</span><br />\n第1回： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/273226/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/273226/</a><br />\n第2回： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/308883/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/308883/</a><br />\n第3回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/320724\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/320724</a><br />\n第4回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/326223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/326223</a><br />\n第5回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/333053\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/333053</a><br />\n第6回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/338526\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/338526</a><br />\n第7回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/342680\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/342680</a><br />\n第8回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/345651\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/345651</a><br />\n第9回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/349635\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/349635</a><br />\n第10回： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/351674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/351674</a><br />\n第11回︰ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/353688\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/353688</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開 Po Template: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc%2Fedit&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4c911f6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc/edit</a><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"54048f7